{"tid":1631372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人組隊圍狗宿？","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:14:09.000Z","uid":287840,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb912a64c067550e6d8c12603e6898c64cbca23","tid":1631372,"uid":287840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明明狗宿遍佈18區，</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係次次18區活動冇人圍狗宿？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明明啲狗至撚驚就係自己乜裝都冇，日常生活俾人搞，</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n吳敢麻包袋，咁圍狗宿夠膽啦掛？(前提係要聚到大數目既街坊，吳係白白送頭)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明明次撚次18區遊行，犬隻第一時間派人守狗宿，一睇就知佢地好撚驚呢樣野，</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明明圍狗宿個時可以撚狗又可以極速散水吳洗送頭，</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n明明可以搞死佢地，可以個個過勞死，<br />\n<br />\n點解吳做？<br />\n<br />\n利申圍過一次，但係之後冇人組織聚吳到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，幾時有個狗宿地圖同圍狗宿時間表？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f6a9f790ff2221a85782efa2788c7c5516648f","tid":1631372,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b37a1e5183a38f28b36c5a8400f1f71925d57aff","tid":1631372,"uid":287840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:23:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"392934a5d9540c65aa670d5c4ff9b9e99c24a6ee","tid":1631372,"uid":287840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb912a64c067550e6d8c12603e6898c64cb